This README file contains information on the contents of the meta-downstream
layer.

Please see the corresponding sections below for details.

Dependencies
============

  URI: https://git.yoctoproject.org/poky/meta
  branch: [same one as checked out for this layer]

Patches
=======

Please submit any patches against the meta-downstream layer via the repository
pull requests (https://github.com/gportay/meta-downstream/pulls).

Bugs
====

Please report any bugs against the meta-downstream layer via the repository
issues (https://github.com/gportay/meta-downstream/issues).

Table of Contents
=================

  I. Adding the meta-downstream layer to your build
 II. Building the firmware

I. Adding the meta-downstream layer to your build
=================================================

Run 'bitbake-layers add-layer meta-downstream'

II. Building the firmware
=========================

Run 'bitbake core-image-minimal'
